      <scopecontent id="aspace_b022b4418355172c204928ec1099e62a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of photographic slides used in the "Class of 1963 40th Reunion Collage," as well as a copy of the final production on videotape (VHS). The material documents the members of the Yale College Class of 1963.</p>  
